game.name: Elsa Ice Skating Injuries
game.description: Cute princess Elsa had a great idea this morning! She used her magical powers to make her personal ice rink and once everything was ready she started enjoying it in a big style. With her purple ice skates on and dressed up really, really nice Princess Elsa started skating around! It was something fun Elsa tried for the first time on her life, but because she was not careful enough she lost balance and injured her foot. Now she needs you as her trustworthy doctor to cure her - can you help her out, ladies? Step in getting the ‘Elsa Skating Injuries’ game started and first of all, help cute Olaf remove Elsa skates. Check out the injuries and then take a pair of sterilized tweezers to remove the little ice pieces that got into her wound. Apply an ice cub over her swelling and then use a cotton ball with some antiseptic solution to clean up her blood and to also disinfect her wound and then bandage it so it can heal. Great job, Doc! Now why don not you ladies go to the next page of the game and find a cute new dress and a matching pair of skates for cute Elsa so she can go skating again? Enjoy playing the ‘Elsa Skating Injuries’ game on DressUpWho.com!
